  "notes": "Chechen in Cyrillic script. Rich ejective series: КӀ, ПӀ, ТӀ, ЦӀ, ЧӀ. ГӀ = pharyngeal /ʕ/; ХЬ = pharyngeal /ħ/; ХӀ = /h/. Front rounded vowels: УЬ = /y/, ОЬ = /wø/, ЭЬ = /ø/. Pharyngeals and ejectives are typologically notable. Complex consonant clusters.",
